<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 20:07:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯播出三名以色列人质在加沙被囚禁的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-of-three-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-captivity/0000018d-473c-d02c-a79f-47bf122b0000</link><description>在视频中，30 岁的兽医护士 Doron Steinbrecher 和 19 岁的以色列国防军士兵 Daniela Gilboa 和 Karina Ariav 表示，他们已被囚禁 107 天</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 19:52:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-of-three-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-captivity/0000018d-473c-d02c-a79f-47bf122b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡谴责国际法院考虑种族灭绝；沙特称以色列“违反”联合国规则，美国称其“毫无根据”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-decries-icj-genocide-mull-u-s-labels-it-unfounded-saudis-note-violations/0000018d-46e2-d35c-a39f-eefaac3f0000</link><description>以色列政治领导人一致谴责法院考虑种族灭绝指控，而巴勒斯坦总理则宣称，“以色列逃避惩罚的日子已经结束了”</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 18:57:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-decries-icj-genocide-mull-u-s-labels-it-unfounded-saudis-note-violations/0000018d-46e2-d35c-a39f-eefaac3f0000</guid></item><item><title>2014年，内塔尼亚胡就哈马斯屠杀阴谋发出预警。九年后，10 月 7 日发生了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-netanyahu-forewarned-of-a-hamas-massacre-plot-nine-years-later-oct-7-happened/0000018d-4591-d02c-a79f-479bf39c0000</link><description>2014年加沙行动前不久，以色列领导人获悉以色列南部计划进行大屠杀，并绑架士兵和平民作为讨价还价的筹码。一名以色列国防军将军当时告诉他的同事，“我不想在周六早上报告五个基布兹已被占领”</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 17:57:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-netanyahu-forewarned-of-a-hamas-massacre-plot-nine-years-later-oct-7-happened/0000018d-4591-d02c-a79f-479bf39c0000</guid></item><item><title>优先考虑人质的以色列人是真正理性的声音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-who-prioritize-the-hostages-are-the-real-voice-of-reason/0000018d-467f-d02c-a79f-47ff7e620000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 17:18:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-who-prioritize-the-hostages-are-the-real-voice-of-reason/0000018d-467f-d02c-a79f-47ff7e620000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院在国际法院就种族灭绝案向以色列发出警告。这就是内塔尼亚胡应该担心的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/icj-fires-israel-a-warning-shot-over-genocide-case-this-is-why-netanyahu-should-worry/0000018d-4625-dc44-a5bf-ceb7d5cf0000</link><description>国际法院周五的临时裁决给以色列带来了好坏参半的消息：尽管以色列没有被告知在加沙停火，但其命令可能会给以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡和他的极右翼部长带来严重的头痛。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 15:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/icj-fires-israel-a-warning-shot-over-genocide-case-this-is-why-netanyahu-should-worry/0000018d-4625-dc44-a5bf-ceb7d5cf0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院裁定以色列必须避免在加沙实施种族灭绝行为，不得下令停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/icj-rules-israel-must-avoid-genocidal-acts-in-gaza-stops-short-of-ordering-cease-fire/0000018d-4606-d35c-a39f-ee5e5b7e0000</link><description>尽管此案的最终裁决可能需要数年时间，但以色列必须履行法院下令的六项临时措施，以保护加沙的巴勒斯坦人，包括提供援助和惩罚煽动种族灭绝的行为</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 15:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/icj-rules-israel-must-avoid-genocidal-acts-in-gaza-stops-short-of-ordering-cease-fire/0000018d-4606-d35c-a39f-ee5e5b7e0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院裁定以色列必须“采取一切措施”避免在加沙发生种族灭绝行为、煽动行为，但不下令停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-live/top-un-court-hands-down-preliminary-ruling-in-south-africa-genocide-case-against-israel/0000018d-451e-dc44-a5bf-cdbeb41c0000</link><description>国际法院初步裁决没有下令停止加沙战争，称以色列必须采取一切措施保护平民，惩罚煽动行为。内塔尼亚胡：法院维护以色列自卫权是正确的，但不应该辩论种族灭绝指控</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 10:44:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-live/top-un-court-hands-down-preliminary-ruling-in-south-africa-genocide-case-against-israel/0000018d-451e-dc44-a5bf-cdbeb41c0000</guid></item><item><title>从否认大屠杀到所有人的大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/from-holocaust-denial-to-everyone-gets-their-own-revisionism-and-relativism-after-oct-7/0000018d-44be-d02c-a79f-47bfbbf80000</link><description>大屠杀的去犹太化和普遍化不可避免地意味着它后来将成为殴打犹太人自己的一根棍子。那些将 10 月 7 日描述为“另一场大屠杀”的人并不好得多</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 09:26:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/from-holocaust-denial-to-everyone-gets-their-own-revisionism-and-relativism-after-oct-7/0000018d-44be-d02c-a79f-47bfbbf80000</guid></item><item><title>美国与以色列建立渠道寻求加沙战争平民死亡问题的答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/u-s-establishes-channel-with-israel-to-seek-answers-on-civilian-deaths-in-gaza-war/0000018d-44a1-dc44-a5bf-ccb744f50000</link><description>据哈马斯卫生部称，以色列针对哈马斯的行动造成了巨大伤亡，拜登政府面临越来越大的压力，此次行动已造成超过 25,000 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 08:14:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/u-s-establishes-channel-with-israel-to-seek-answers-on-civilian-deaths-in-gaza-war/0000018d-44a1-dc44-a5bf-ccb744f50000</guid></item><item><title>随着内塔尼亚胡的失败不断累积，以色列总理的信用丧失带来了更大的危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/as-netanyahus-failings-pile-up-israels-out-of-credit-pm-poses-even-greater-danger/0000018d-4252-d02c-a79f-43db08760000</link><description>从人质危机到哈马斯垮台，现在是时候说出众所周知的事情了：内塔尼亚胡不可能获胜。与此同时，塔利·戈特利夫（Tally Gotliv）是他的政党在议会中最新的破坏者</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 04:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/as-netanyahus-failings-pile-up-israels-out-of-credit-pm-poses-even-greater-danger/0000018d-4252-d02c-a79f-43db08760000</guid></item><item><title>退伍前夕，以色列士兵谈论战斗、人质以及他们进入加沙的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/on-eve-of-discharge-israeli-soldiers-talk-combat-hostages-and-why-they-went-into-gaza/0000018d-421a-dc44-a5bf-cabedf330000</link><description>戈拉尼旅士兵获得了为期一周的休假，在此期间他们讨论了在加沙的三个月不间断的战斗。 与此同时，以色列军方发起了一场针对国家审计长的运动，后者希望调查以色列国防军对 10 月 7 日及之后的处理方式</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 04:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/on-eve-of-discharge-israeli-soldiers-talk-combat-hostages-and-why-they-went-into-gaza/0000018d-421a-dc44-a5bf-cabedf330000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩报道：以色列袭击造成两人死亡；哈马斯播出加沙人质视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-live/report-u-s-sets-up-channel-with-israel-seeking-answers-on-civilian-casualties/0000018d-43b5-dc44-a5bf-cbb79fb40000</link><description>美国因涉嫌参与 10 月 7 日袭击的员工而暂停向近东救济工程处提供资金 ■ 人质家属试图在凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点阻止人道主义援助进入加沙 ■ 资料来源：以色列、哈马斯就人质交易的大部分问题达成基本谅解 ■ 哈马斯加沙卫生部报告称，加沙死亡人数已超过 26,000 人</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 03:13:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-live/report-u-s-sets-up-channel-with-israel-seeking-answers-on-civilian-casualties/0000018d-43b5-dc44-a5bf-cbb79fb40000</guid></item><item><title>“我相信相亲。从各个方面来说这都是一笔交易，就像买一辆车一样”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-26/ty-article/.highlight/i-believe-in-matchmaking-its-a-transaction-in-every-respect-like-buying-a-car/0000018d-4356-d02c-a79f-43df4ce90000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一位正在寻找合适对象的老师和一位将自己定义为“带着小提琴的流浪犹太人”的自由程序员</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 01:36:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-26/ty-article/.highlight/i-believe-in-matchmaking-its-a-transaction-in-every-respect-like-buying-a-car/0000018d-4356-d02c-a79f-43df4ce90000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡，有了你，我们就失去了一切。痛苦是无限的。没有你才有希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/weve-lost-everything-the-pain-is-infinite-only-without-netanayhu-will-there-be-hope/0000018d-4200-d02c-a79f-439b04970000</link><description>10 月 7 日，Reuma 和 Gadi Kedem 失去了他们的女儿、女婿和三个小孙子——全部在基布兹 Nir ​​Oz 的家中被谋杀。现在他们希望一件事：看到内塔尼亚胡被赶下台</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 01:09:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/weve-lost-everything-the-pain-is-infinite-only-without-netanayhu-will-there-be-hope/0000018d-4200-d02c-a79f-439b04970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方表示，尽管人质死亡，但针对哈马斯领导人的政策没有改变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-say-no-change-in-policy-of-targeting-hamas-leaders-despite-hostage-deaths/0000018d-4253-d35c-a39f-ea5b514d0000</link><description>三名人质在哈马斯指挥官袭击地点附近被囚禁。以色列军队表示，他们可能因吸入爆炸产生的二次化学反应而释放的有毒气体而死亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 23:01:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-say-no-change-in-policy-of-targeting-hamas-leaders-despite-hostage-deaths/0000018d-4253-d35c-a39f-ea5b514d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国和以色列在加沙战争中敲定重大军用飞机交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/u-s-and-israel-finalize-major-military-aircraft-deals-amid-gaza-war/0000018d-4234-d35c-a39f-ea7e5b8c0000</link><description>随着加沙战争进入第五个月，与真主党全面战争的准备工作正在进行中，以色列预计将利用美国援助资金购买两个中队的战斗机和一个中队的攻击直升机</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 21:05:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/u-s-and-israel-finalize-major-military-aircraft-deals-amid-gaza-war/0000018d-4234-d35c-a39f-ea7e5b8c0000</guid></item><item><title>共和党人正在研究内塔尼亚胡如何打击拜登的战后加沙计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/republicans-are-looking-at-netanyahu-for-how-to-combat-bidens-post-war-gaza-plans/0000018d-4162-d35c-a39f-eb7a4a6e0000</link><description>随着拜登政府敦促以色列结束对加沙的地面入侵，并展望巴勒斯坦权力机构掌管的可能未来，美国共和党人正在陷入共和党风格的困境</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 20:10:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/republicans-are-looking-at-netanyahu-for-how-to-combat-bidens-post-war-gaza-plans/0000018d-4162-d35c-a39f-eb7a4a6e0000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列和哈马斯推进人质协议，停火仍然是争论的焦点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/cease-fire-remains-bone-of-contention-as-israel-and-hamas-advance-toward-hostage-deal/0000018d-41b7-d02c-a79f-43bf13c30000</link><description>据熟悉谈判的消息人士透露，双方已就协议的大部分条款达成基本协议，“但需要解决的核心问题是哈马斯坚持的全面停火问题”</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 19:12:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/cease-fire-remains-bone-of-contention-as-israel-and-hamas-advance-toward-hostage-deal/0000018d-41b7-d02c-a79f-43bf13c30000</guid></item><item><title>是的，与杀人犯和平相处</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/yes-peace-is-made-with-murderers/0000018d-4133-d02c-a79f-43bb6cc80000</link><description>大多数解决民族冲突的协议都无法经受住时间的考验。对那些成功人士的研究揭示了其中的秘密：他们都是从监狱里出来的。以色列需要在加沙战争“后一天”考虑这一点</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 18:55:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/yes-peace-is-made-with-murderers/0000018d-4133-d02c-a79f-43bb6cc80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡办公室同意“泄露”总理抨击卡塔尔的录音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-okayed-leaked-recording-of-him-bashing-qatar/0000018d-4160-d35c-a39f-eb7af9c60000</link><description>如果内塔尼亚胡总理认为这符合以色列的最佳利益和外交政策，这并不是内塔尼亚胡办公室第一次批准有关敏感安全问题的报道</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 18:01:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-okayed-leaked-recording-of-him-bashing-qatar/0000018d-4160-d35c-a39f-eb7af9c60000</guid></item></channel></rss>